opendial.domains.rules.parameters

Class CompositeParameter

  • java.lang.Object
    • opendial.domains.rules.parameters.CompositeParameter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Parameter

    public class CompositeParameter
extends java.lang.Object
implements Parameter
    Parameter represented as a combination of several continuous parameters. The combination may either take the form of a linear combination or a multiplication.
    Version:
    $Date:: 2014-11-03 16:02:29 #$
    Author:
